Package: runinpower
Title: Clinical Trial Power Analysis with Run-In Observations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ronald G.", "Thomas", email = "rthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Power analysis methodology for clinical trials with one or more
    run-in observations. Focuses on optimal use of baseline rate information
    in longitudinal designs, particularly for Alzheimer's disease trials where
    the outcome is a rate of change.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Imports:
    renv,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
